item.title: Getting your fill of Reverse Engineering and Malware Analysis

item.description: Matt, from the Exotic Liability forums, posed a suggestion for a episode: “Getting started [in] reverse engineering hardware drivers?”. I thought this was an interesting topic to attack so, I dug a bit into my RSS feed pile of goo and compiled this list of links. Hope this helps Matt.
